data.description: Nestled in Poet's Corner of Big Bear City, 308 Bluebill is a charming mountain retreat offering a perfect escape. With rustic charm and modern amenities, this property is an ideal year-round getaway for nature enthusiasts. Surrounded by tall pine trees, you will enjoy a a picturesque landscape. The spacious front deck allows for outdoor gatherings. The open-concept living area is filled with natural light and centered around a cozy stone fireplace. The kitchen is well-equipped with modern appliances and a breakfast bar. The bedrooms are comfortable, this home provides a peaceful retreat for all. The bathrooms are well-appointed and provide convenience. This home is a serene mountain retreat with a blend of rustic appeal and modern comforts. Ideal for nature lovers, this property offers a tranquil escape in a beautiful setting.
